<p>To add strings to the <gui>Translation Memory</gui> from existing PO files:</p>

<list type="numbered">
      <item><p>Press the menu button in the top-right corner of the window and select <gui style="menuitem">Build translation memory</gui>.</p></item>
      <item><p>Select the folder where the PO files are stored.</p></item>
      <item><p>If the folder also contains PO files for other languages, select <gui>Use only files with this name</gui> and enter a file name (like <file>xy.po</file>). If you do not do this, then your translation memory will also contain translations for these other languages as it will import all PO files in the folder.</p></item>
      <item><p>Select the folder where the PO files are stored, and press <gui style="button">Add to Database</gui>.</p></item>
      <item><p>Press <gui style="button">Close</gui> to finish.</p></item>
</list>

